The paper deals with the analysis of cooperative wireless networks over fading channels with imperfect CSI and node mobility. This topic falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses power allocation and optimization, which falls under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Communications (cs.COMM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses mathematical modeling and analysis, which falls under the Mathematics of Computing (cs.MA) sub-category.
